data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select tt.ten, td.tenkho, ngayhoso, tenvacxin, nguyennhan, tdoi.ngaytheodoi, tinhtrang, huongxuly from test_theodoi as tdoi inner join test_tondong as td on tdoi.tondong_id = td.id inner join trungtam as tt on td.trungtam_id = tt.id where td.hoantat = 0 and month(ngaytheodoi) = (@pmThang) and year(ngaytheodoi) = (@pmNam) order by ngaytheodoi DESC, td.trungtam_id ASC, ngayhoso ASC
